                    <ul><li>Please visit the link:&nbsp;<a href="about:blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(3, 102, 214);">click here</a></li><li>And find: Automatic downloads</li><li>Select: alow</li></ul><p><br></p>
